    &kp LSHFT    &kp Z          &kp X         &kp C       &kp V              &kp B                     &none         &none          &kp TAB         &none     &none   &kp CAPS      &none         &none                            &kp N       &kp M      &kp COMMA   &kp DOT     &kp FSLH        &kp RSHFT
